<p><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20230307000403/https://hansard.parliament.uk/search/Debates?house=commons" onclick="__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'https://web.archive.org/web/20230307000403/https://hansard.parliament.uk/search/Debates?house=commons', 'Hansard Online.');"><span data-contrast="none">Hansard Online.</span></a></p>
<p><span data-contrast="none">Robert Rhodes James, ed., </span><i><span data-contrast="none">Winston S. Churchill: His Complete Speeches 1928-1935</span></i><span data-contrast="none">, 6 vols. New York: Bowker, 1974, vol. VI.</span><span data-ccp-props="{}"> </span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="none">David Lough, </span><i><span data-contrast="none">No More Champagne: Churchill and His Money</span></i><span data-contrast="none">. New York: Picador, 2015.</span><span data-ccp-props="{}"> </span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="none">Andrew Roberts, </span><i><span data-contrast="none">Churchill: Walking with Destiny</span></i><span data-contrast="none">. New York: Viking, 2018.</span></p>
<p><em>The Times</em> (London) Digital Archive.</p>
